Package: Natura2014
Type: Package
Title: Forest growth simulator Natura-2014
Version: 2.2.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Isabelle", "Auger", email = "isabelle.auger@mrnf.gouv.qc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Mathieu", "Fortin", email = "mathieu.fortin@nrcan-rncan.gc.ca", role = c("ctb")))
Description: Natura-2014 is a stand level forest growth model based on stand age.
    It uses merchantable stand characteristics at age t to predict them at time age+10 years.
	  The model predict number of trees, basal area and volume for 5 species groups (tolerant hardwood,
	  intolerant harwood, tolerant softwood, intolerant softwood, balsam fir). The model can only run
	  in deterministic mode.
